<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4890585>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Evolutionary relationships of sampled Hippasterinae (Goniasteridae) based on 654 aligned nucleotide positions of the cytochrome c oxidase subunit I gene. The phylogenetic tree was inferred using the neighbour-joining method (Saitou & Nei, 1987) in MEGA v. 5.2.1 (Tamura et al., 2011). The bootstrap consensus tree inferred from 500 replicates was drawn to scale, with distances computed using the maximum composite likelihood method (Tamura et al., 2004), in units of numbers of base substitutions per site. Ambiguous positions were removed for each pair of sequences prior to calculating the distance matrix. Terminals were labelled with GenBank accession numbers and (where available) with museum voucher numbers. Bootstrap support values are shown above or below branches when greater than 70%." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4890585/files/figure.png" .

